text: Mingo is an unincorporated town in Tulsa County, Oklahoma. It has a population of 22. ==Geography== Mingo is located at . It has a total area of 0.8 miles, all land. Mingo is also 600 feet above sea level. Mingo is located at 46th St N and Mingo Road. It is located northeast of the Tulsa International Airport ==References== Category:Geography of Tulsa County, Oklahoma
title: Mingo, Oklahoma
